14. INTERVIEW TRAPS

---

* Catching Exception everywhere
* Ignoring exception (empty catch)
* Not using finally for cleanup
* Printing only e.getMessage() (loses stack trace)

---

15. FINAL UNDERSTANDING

---

* Exceptions = control flow for errors
* Use specific handling
* Keep code clean + safe
* Design matters more than syntax


